Cytometry analysis pipeline for large and complex datasets


MAIN COMPUTATION SCRIPT
    CAPXpipe:           Ctrl panel, data management, parameter select, FlowSOM, tSNE, tSNEplots

FURTHER INTERPRETATION
    ColRandom:          Colour clusters (random colours)
    ColSpecific:        Colour clusters (specific colours)
    PopName:            Add population name and number to files
    HeatmapMFI:         Generate a heatmap visualising MFI patterns

SAMPLE CHANGES OVER CONDITIONS
    Condense:           Condense data to number of cells (in each cluster or pop) per sample
    HeatmapFOLD:        Generate a heatmap visualising fold-change
    AutoGraph:          Automated generation of point graphs to examine group differences
